snippet.title: Papa's Quiz - Trailer
snippet.description:
Papa’s Quiz is a party game for 1-8 players. Use phones or tablets as controllers and compete in multiple question types, where the smartest and fastest player will be the last standing victor!

Available on:

Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1484730/Papas_Quiz/
Playstation - https://store.playstation.com/sv-se/product/EP6591-CUSA27020_00-2472935406749361
XBOX - https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/p/papas-quiz/9nl18bgsls95
Nintendo Switch - https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/papas-quiz-switch/
